node.text: Pumpkins! Spice! And everything nice! I’m excited to be partnering with @VarsityTutors again on September 9th for a free, live class where we’ll draw an iconic fall character together. Join me to learn techniques for designing characters and drawing features that give them the personality you want—no, need—them to have. Link in bio! #varsitytutors

node.text: I’m so excited to partner with @varsitytutors to teach a couple interactive classes! Come draw with me! Join me and @VarsityTutors on July 19th for my free, live draw-along as we explore the art of drawing human faces and making them come alive. You’ll leave class with an animated character of your own, plus collaborate with me to create the ultimate character to define “summer.” Bring your pens, pencils, curiosity and creativity. Sign up today! Link in bio!  #VarsityTutors #AD
